overview: Family Over Riches presents 810TRAP, which is a dark descriptive film about violence in Flint, Michigan starring Family Over Riches artist "Messo". This film depicts two people from different sides of town who have a conflict of interest in street matters. The two agree to resolve the issue, but one of the person's friends who was supposed to be involved with the resolution disagrees, convincing his friend to resort to other options.
title: 810 Trap
